Package scene.controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardController
    The controller(C in MVC pattern) of the board.
    EndSceneController
    The controller (C in MVC) of EndSceneView which sets event handlers for buttons in view.
    GameLevelController
    It updates the board and animal when player gets to the next level.
    GameMusicPlayer
    The GameMusicPlayer plays music when a game starts and stop music when a game stops.
    GameSceneController
    The controller (C in MVC pattern) of the game scene.
    GameTimer
    The timer of the game.
    HistorySceneController
    The controller (C in MVC) of HistorySceneView which sets event handlers for buttons in view.
    InfoSceneController
    The controller (C in MVC) of StartSceneView which sets event handlers for buttons in view.
    StartSceneController
    The controller (C in MVC) of StartSceneView which sets event handlers for buttons in view.
    WorldListener
    The controller class controls the world that passed to it.
